==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shole
<hw>Shole</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A plank fixed beneath an
object, as beneath the rudder of a vessel, to protect it from injury; a
plank on the ground under the end of a shore or the like.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shole</ent>⟦br⟧

